data.description: Step into the 2 story hardwood floor foyer with spectacular open staircase.  To the left there is a living room and to the right there is a formal dining room.  Go into the kitchen, there you will find a gorgeous kitchen with L-shaped eat-at island, and tons of cabinets, and counter top work space.  The sunroom can be used as a dining area, if desired. The large family room, open to the kitchen, can fit lots of furniture and the electric fireplace adds great ambiance.   There is also a half bath for convenience.  Upstairs, the owners suite has double closets and a private bath with corner soaking tub, and double sinks.  There are 4 more bedrooms on this level with, SURPRISE, one can be a 2nd owners suite with its own private full bathroom.  The main bathroom finishes up this level.  The lower level has a great family/game/rec room, and another half bath.  Out back there is a trek deck with Sunsetter shade keeping the outdoor times, cooler.  Added bonus....the shed conveys.   Hurry, don't wait to see this move in ready home and make it yours!
